uk.ac.manchester.cs.hobo.model.motor

Class DModelMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.manchester.cs.hobo.model.motor.DModelMap

  • public class DModelMap
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents all required mappings between specific entities in the Object Model (OM) and correponding entities in any external sources that will also be contributing towards the Frames Model (FM).

        Parameters:
        mapper - Class-mapper to be added

      • labelsFromDirectClasses

        public boolean labelsFromDirectClasses()
        Specifies whether, for those OM classes that are mapped to entities from external sources, the bound CFrame objects will obtain their labels from the relevant OM class-names, rather than from the mapped entities. A label taken from an OM class-name will be a heuristically-modified version of the leaf class-name.
        Returns:
        True if frame-labels will come from the OM classes

      • labelsFromDirectFields

        public boolean labelsFromDirectFields()
        Specifies whether, for those OM fields that are mapped to entities from external sources, the bound CSlot objects will obtain their labels from the relevant OM field-names, rather than from the mapped entities. A label taken from an OM field-name will be a heuristically-modified version of the field-name.
        Returns:
        True if slot-labels will come from the OM fields

      • getClassMap

        public DClassMap getClassMap(java.lang.Class<? extends DObject> dClass)
        Retrieves a set of mappings between a specified OM class and correponding entities from external sources, if such mappings exist.
        Parameters:
        dClass - OM class for which mapping is required
        Returns:
        Required class-map object, or null if not found
